{"title":"深圳散步（外一首）","authors":["黎焕颐"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":6,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳散步（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎焕颐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五千年寂寞，春归无主。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南国红豆，岁岁相思——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想得好苦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是的，苦到沸点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思便成熟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！成熟的相思——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成熟的苦炼之树："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如同修篁，如同芭蕉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎风吐秀，次第出土……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才十年呵！布谷声声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声烟柳润如酥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这有缺陷的世界呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么需要创新，并且互补。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互补吧！——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上没有绝对的乐园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间没有绝对的净土。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史如是说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"净土不净是为常青的菩提树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史又如是说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菩提有树，过净则枯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇污则腐……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！在深圳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我获得一片悟性的沃土！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活力·喷吐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳在跑步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而我，在深圳散步。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多不协调呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许，我真的落伍？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全民、集体、个体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争门户！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争时间！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争速度！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争开拓！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争胜负！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛所有地心的活力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在这里争着喷吐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！一个争字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活了财路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活了思路……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路在何处？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一跨出罗浮桥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是香江烟火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相距，只隔一步！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过去吗？不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个国家两种制度。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳，你之所有，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是香港之所无。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"香港之所有，正是你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有的桎梏……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才十年呵！声光化电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化来不夜的莺歌燕舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才十年呵！大厦参天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云鹏震羽，邀来八方商贾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才十年呵！一片新生林带"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一片新桃换旧符……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快哉！十年风起于罗湖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吹皱十亿池塘——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池塘春水漾新绿……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快哉！快哉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云蒸霞蔚，珠归南浦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"方圆不到２０公里的小镇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜之间，举世瞩目！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞩目吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五千年的负数，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深圳只用十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便一一弥补，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并且以亿为单位，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一一偿付给罗湖……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哎！这是怎样的时速？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是怎样的加减乘除？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怕电子计算机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也难以作满意的答复。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，我跑到市政大厦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去问孺子牛。谁说不是呢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有她一清二楚……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}